  "text": "ILC chimerism was then determined by assessing HLA class I expression by a pan anti-class I antibody versus an HLA allele group-specific marker. For patients [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] 13 , and 14, recipient cells were distinguished from donor by HLA A2/A28 expression. For patient 7, donor but not recipient cells expressed HLA B8. For patient 9, recipient but not donor cells expressed HLA A9. Figure 1F shows a representative chimerism plot.",
